<div id="outline-container-sec-6" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-6"><span class="section-number-2">6</span> Storage</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-6">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-6-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-6-1"><span class="section-number-3">6.1</span> hardware</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-6-1">
<p>
S3 bucket
添付ファイル保存に用いる
</p>

<p>
各種環境様のbucketを要する
</p>
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>production
</li>
<li>pre-release
</li>
<li>staging
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-6-2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-6-2"><span class="section-number-3">6.2</span> setting</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-6-2">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>S3専用IAMの作成
IAM policyへS3のアクセス権を付与する。
</li>
</ul>

<p>
以下、IAMへのpolicy設定例
</p>
<hr  />
<p>
{
    "Version": "2012-10-17",
    "Statement": [
        {
            "Effect": "Allow",
            "Action": [
                "s3:*"
            ],
            "Resource": [
                "arn:aws:s3:::development-ruby-dev-allin-sns",
                "arn:aws:s3:::development-ruby-dev-allin-sns/*",
                "arn:aws:s3:::staging-ruby-dev-allin-sns",
                "arn:aws:s3:::staging-ruby-dev-allin-sns/*",
                "arn:aws:s3:::ruby-dev-allin-sns",
                "arn:aws:s3:::ruby-dev-allin-sns/*",
                "*"
            ]
        }
    ]
}
</p>
<hr  />
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-6-3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-6-3"><span class="section-number-3">6.3</span> data抽出</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-6-3">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>IAMのクレデンシャル (app serverの環境変数へ設定)
</li>
<li>bucket names (app serverの環境変数へ設定)
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7" class="outline-2">
<h2 id="sec-7"><span class="section-number-2">7</span> app server</h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-7">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-7-1" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-7-1"><span class="section-number-3">7.1</span> hardware</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-7-1">
<p>
ec2 instance
</p>

<ul class="org-ul">
<li>t2.small : 1台
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-2" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-7-2"><span class="section-number-3">7.2</span> software</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-7-2">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>centos 6.7 (or 6.5)
</li>
<li>nodebrew
</li>
<li>nodejs v5.6.0
</li>
<li>npm packages (local)
deploy時、自動install
</li>

<li>npm packages (global)
pm2
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3" class="outline-3">
<h3 id="sec-7-3"><span class="section-number-3">7.3</span> setting</h3>
<div class="outline-text-3" id="text-7-3">
</div><div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-1" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-1"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.1</span> SE linux</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-1">
<p>
disable se linux
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-2" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-2"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.2</span> install package</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-2">
<p>
$ sudo yum install perl git
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-3" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-3"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.3</span> user追加</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-3">
<p>
$ useradd node
$ sudo su - node
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-4" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-4"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.4</span> make nodejs dir</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-4">
<p>
$ sudo mkdir  <i>var/node</i>
$ sudo chown node:node <i>var/node</i>
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-5" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-5"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.5</span> ssh</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-5">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>github鍵を設置
</li>
<li>user centosのauthorized<sub>keyを、user</sub> nodeへcopy
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-6" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-6"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.6</span> setup nodejs</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-6">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>nodejs
<ul class="org-ul">
<li><code>[&#xa0;]</code> : install nodebrew
$ curl -L git.io/nodebrew | perl - setup
$ export PATH=$HOME/.nodebrew/current/bin:$PATH
$ echo 'export PATH=$HOME/.nodebrew/current/bin:$PATH' &gt;&gt; ~/.bashrc
</li>

<li><code>[&#xa0;]</code> : install nodejs
$ nodebrew install-binary v5.6.0;
$ nodebrew use v5.6.0
</li>
</ul>
</li>

<li>npm install global
$ npm install pm2 -g
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-7" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-7"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.7</span> ssl証明書</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-7">
<p>
$ cd <i>home/node/ssl</i>
</p>

<p>
./server.key # 鍵
./cert       # 証明書
./ca         # 中間証明書
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-8" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-8"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.8</span> 環境変数 -</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-8">
<p>
export AWS<sub>ACCESS</sub><sub>KEY</sub><sub>ID</sub>=[id]
export AWS<sub>SECRET</sub><sub>ACCESS</sub><sub>KEY</sub>=[key]
</p>

<p>
export SSL<sub>KEY</sub><sub>PATH</sub>=/home/node/ssl/server.key
export SSL<sub>CERT</sub><sub>PATH</sub>=/home/node/ssl/cert
export SSL<sub>CA</sub><sub>PATH</sub>=/home/node/ssl/ca
</p>

<p>
export REDIS<sub>URL</sub>=allin-sns.hc7k9f.0001.apne1.cache.amazonaws.com
export REDIS<sub>PASS</sub>=''
</p>

<p>
export MONGO<sub>URL</sub>="mongodb://10.0.1.100:27017/sns-development,10.0.1.101:27017/sns-development,10.0.1.103:27017/sns-development"
export MONGO<sub>USER</sub>=''
export MONGO<sub>PASS</sub>=''
</p>

<p>
export AUTH<sub>SERVER</sub><sub>URL</sub>=<a href="http://all-in.xyz/">http://all-in.xyz/</a>
</p>

<p>
export S3<sub>BUCKET</sub>=production-all-in-sns
</p>
</div>
</div>

<div id="outline-container-sec-7-3-9" class="outline-4">
<h4 id="sec-7-3-9"><span class="section-number-4">7.3.9</span> deploy from local</h4>
<div class="outline-text-4" id="text-7-3-9">
<ul class="org-ul">
<li>install pm2
$ npm install pm2 -g
</li>

<li>write host to ssh config
<p>
$ vi ~/.ssh.config
</p>
<hr  />
<p>
Host allin-sns-[ENV]<sub>001</sub>
    user          centos
    port          22
    Hostname      [IP]
    IdentityFile  ~/.ssh/allin-sns-demo.pem
</p>
<hr  />
</li>

<li>run init deploy
$ cd [allin-sns dir]

<p>
$ pm2 deploy ./app/config/deploy/deploy.json [ENV] setup
$ pm2 deploy ./app/config/deploy/deploy.json [ENV] update &#x2013;force
</p>
</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
